Jo-Israel otimo winjruok gi Nyasaye


1  Noyudo ka Ruoth Nyasaye osewacho ni Musa niya, “Bi ira e got, kaachiel gi Harun gi Nadab gi Abihu kod jodong Israel piero abiriyo, to kapok uchopo machiegni, kulreuru mondo ulem. 
2  In kendi, Musa, ema nichop machiegni koda. Jomokogo ok nosud ira, to bende onge ng’ato ang’ata ma noidh kodi ku.”


3  Musa nodhi monyiso ji chike kod buche duto mag Ruoth Nysaye. Ji duto nodwoke niya, “Wayie timo gik moko duto ma Ruoth Nyasaye osewacho.” 
4  Musa nondiko chike duto mag Ruoth Nyasaye. To kinyne gokinyi nogero kendo-mar-misango e tiend got, kendo nochungo kite apar gariyo mag rapar, maromre gi kar romb dhout Israel apar gariyo. 
5  Eka nooro yawuowi moko ma jo-Israel monego rwedhi, mi gitimogo ni Ruoth Nyasaye misengni miwang’o pep, kod misengni mag sawo. 
6  Musa nokawo remo moko, moolo e tewni, to remo modong’ nokiro e kendo mar-misango. 
7  Bang’e nokawo kitabu mondikie weche mag singruokgo, mosomo matek mondo ji duto owinji. Giduto ne giwacho niya, “Wayie winjo Ruoth Nyasaye, kendo wanatim duto mosechiko.” 
8  

Bang’ mano Musa nokawo remo, mokiro kuom ji, kowacho niya, “Ma e remo mar singruok mane Ruoth Nyasaye osemiyo utimo kode, kaluwore gi weche manie kitabuni.”


9  Musa gi Harun gi Nadab kod Abihu, kaachiel gi jodong Israel piero abiriyo nodhi e got, moneno Nyasach Israel. 
10  Nochung’ ewi gima chalo gi laro molos gi kit ombo marieny mana ka polo. 
11  To Ruoth Nyasaye ne ok ohinyo jodong Israelgo. Ne gineno Ruoth Nyasaye, mi gichiemo kode kendo gimetho.

Musa e got Sinai


12  Ruoth Nyasaye nowacho ni Musa niya, “Bi ira e got ku, mondo ibed ka. Abiro miyi kite mopamore ma asendikoe buche kod chike mondo ipuonj ji.” 
13  Musa kaachiel gi Joshua jatichne nodhi e god Nyasaye. 
14  Noyudo Musa osewacho ni jodong Israel niya, “Ritwauru ka, nyaka waduogi. Harun kod Hur eki odong’ kodu. Ng’ato ka ng’ato man gi wach modwaro loso to mondo odhi irgi.”


15  Kamano Musa nodhi ewi got, kendo bor polo noimo got. 
16  Duong’ maler mar Ruoth Nyasaye nolor ewi got Sinai, mi bor polo noimo got kuom ndalo auchiel. To chieng’ mar abiriyo Ruoth Nyasaye noluongo Musa gi e bor polo. 
17  Duong’ maler mar Ruoth Nyasaye ne chalo ni jo-Israel mana ka mach maduong’ maliel ewi got. 
18  

Musa nodonjo e bor polono, modhi ewi got, kendo nobet kuno kuom ndalo piero ang’wen odiechieng gotieno.

